HEADWORD: Objectionable
<hw>Ob*jec"tion*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Liable to
objection; likely to be objected to or disapproved of; offensive;
<as>as, <ex>objectionable</ex> words</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ob*jec"tion*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
